Product Name: Craftsman 50 ft. L X 3/8 in. D Rubber Air Hose 300 psi Black
Description:
The CRAFTSMAN 3/8-in x 50-ft Rubber Air Hose is built to handle the toughest work environments. This contractor-grade air hose is made from durable, oil and abrasion-resistant rubber that withstands harsh conditions while retaining flexibility, even in temperatures as low as 30 degrees F. With a maximum working pressure of 300 PSI, it is compatible with most air compressors and pneumatic tools. The 1/4-in NPT fittings make for easy connection to quick-connect plugs and couplers (not included), while the 50-ft length provides ample reach. Ideal for automotive, garage, and workshop use, this air hose delivers reliable performance for professionals and DIY users alike.
50-ft hose designed for heavy-duty use in tough work environments, offering long-lasting durability
Retains flexibility even in temperatures as low as 30 degrees F, ensuring reliable performance in any weather
Made from durable rubber that resists abrasions and oil, extending the lifespan of the hose
Engineered to resist twisting and kinking, allowing for uninterrupted airflow and smoother operation
Equipped with 1/4-in male NPT threads that easily connect to quick-connect plugs and couplers (quick-connects not included)
Ideal for automotive, garage, and other workshop tasks requiring high-performance air tools
Handles up to 300 PSI, compatible with most air compressors and pneumatic tools
Operates in temperatures from 30 degrees F to 200 degrees F, making it suitable for year-round use
Lightweight design makes it easy to handle and position, even during long periods of use

Product Name: Crescent Wiss 9-3/4 in. Stainless Steel Left Compound Action Aviation Snips 18 Ga. 1 pk
Description:
Crescent Wiss has taken the Aviation Snip to the next level with the advanced Metal Master Aviation Snips. The precision-cast molybdenum blades have CNC-ground serrations which allow for more uniform serrations that provide a cleaner cut every time. They feature extended pivot bolt life due to the superior free-float design. The spring-action design allows for fast, effortless feed. The all-new latch design provides ergonomic single-handed operation for left or right handed users. New extended non-slip handle grips give users better control while cutting. The new generation of Crescent Wiss Metal Master will cut over 8 miles of steel and feature up to 10 times longer cut life than traditional Aviation Snips. They are available in left/straight cut, right/straight cut and straight cut.
Ergonomic, single material non-slip handle grips provide easy cleaning with built-in hang hole for convenient storage
Cuts left from tight curves to straight with red handles for quick identification
Made in the USA
Cuts up to 18 gauge low carbon, rolled steel
Tested up to 500,000 cuts, engineered for superior cutting performance
Superior design requires 20% less force to cut
Ultra durable pivot bolt design provides a longer cutting life
Precision ground, serrated blades allow for enhanced material control
Spring loaded return for easy use
Single-handed latch operation for left or right-handed use

Product Name: Craftsman 6.75 in. D Fine Dust Wet/Dry Vac Cartridge Filter 5-20 gal 1 pc
Description:
The CRAFTSMAN Fine Dust Filter for wet/dry vacs is designed to tackle job cleanups like mold, cold ashes, and everyday dirt like sawdust, wood chips, jobsite debris and car or truck dirt. This efficient 3-layer cartridge filter helps reduce blockage. Removing and installing wet/dry vacuum filters is quick, easy and secure. For added convenience, the filter material can be washed with water and reused once fully dried. Compatible with all current CRAFTSMAN shop vacs 5 gallon and larger. This filter allows you to be prepared for a variety of projects. Regularly replacing the filter helps ensure maximum performance and enhances the life of your wet/dry vac. For wet pickup, use the CRAFTSMAN Wet Application Filter (CMXZVBE38773; sold separately).
FITS: 5 gallon to 20 gallon CRAFTSMAN vacs made 1988 and after

The precision-cast molybdenum blades have CNC-ground serrations which allow for more uniform serrations that provide a cleaner cut every time. The all-new latch design provides ergonomic single-handed operation for left or right handed users. New extended non-slip handle grips give users better control while cutting. The new generation of Crescent Wiss Metal Master will cut over 8 miles of steel and feature up to 10 times longer cut life than traditional Aviation Snips. They are available in left/straight cut, right/straight cut and straight cut.

The Milwaukee Type 2, Class C Black Safety Helmet delivers better protection and more comfort. The safety helmet offers protection from top and side impacts. These construction safety helmets are Bolt accessory compatible with four Bolt accessory slots and two universal accessory slots that easily integrate additional personal protection equipment and accessories to secure accessories simultaneously. This Milwaukee helmet has a comfortable padded suspension that includes an adjustable swinging ratchet for better comfort. The DeWalt DCN660 16 Gauge angled finish nails from 1-1/4 in. to 2-1/2 in. which makes it ideal for fastening crown molding, casing and baseboards. Inline magazine provides easy use in multiple orientations and in tight spaces

Description:
3M Particulate Respirator 8200/07023 (AAD), N95 is an economical, disposable particulate respirator that is designed to help provide reliable respiratory protection of at least 95 percent filtration efficiency against certain non oil based particles. This respirator is designed for use for particles such as those from grinding, sanding, sweeping, sawing, bagging or processing minerals, coal, iron ore, flour, metal, wood, pollen and certain other substances. The MILWAUKEE Type 2, Class E White Safety Helmet delivers users better protection and more comfort. The safety helmet offers protection from top and side impacts. These construction safety helmets are BOLT Accessory Compatible with four BOLT accessory slots and two universal accessory slots that easily integrate additional personal protection equipment and accessories so users can Secure Accessories Simultaneously. An antimicrobial sweatband and helmet liner prevent odor and bacteria build up and are removable and machine washable. These safety helmets are ANSI type 2.

Description:
The Milwaukee M18 Fuel 16-inch chainsaw delivers the power to cut hardwoods, cuts faster than gas and delivers up to 150 cuts per charge. Provide the power and performance of a gas engine up to 40CC. The unit is designed to meet the performance, durability and ergonomic needs of professional landscape maintenance, power utility and the installed M18 user. The Powerstate brushless motor maintains speed under heavy loads without bogging down to outperform small gas engines and higher voltage systems. Redlink Plus intelligence ensures maximum performance and protection from overload, overheating and over-discharge. The M18 RedLithium high output HD12.0 battery delivers unmatched run-time in all applications. M18 Fuel technology allows the unit to reach full throttle in under 1 second providing ultimate control and productivity.

Provides 50 percent more power and runs 50 percent cooler versus standard red lithium HD packs

Compatible with all M18 batteries

Product Name: 3M N95 Paint Sanding Cup Disposable Respirator Pro-Series Valved White 10 pc
Description:
3M Particulate Respirator 8511, N95 is a disposable particulate respirator that is designed to help provide reliable respiratory protection of at least 95 percent filtration efficiency against certain non oil based particles. The respirator is designed for use for particles such as those from grinding, sanding, sweeping, sawing, bagging or other dusty operations. This respirator can also help reduce inhalation exposures to certain airborne biological particles (examples: mold, bacillus anthracis, mycobacterium tuberculosis), but cannot eliminate the risk of contracting infection, illness or disease. The respirator incorporates 3M proprietary technology with advanced electrostatically charged microfiber filter media designed for ease of breathing. This respirator is compatible with a variety of protective eyewear and hearing protection. Fitted with a 3M cool flow exhalation valve, this respirator is ideally suited for work situations involving heat, humidity or long periods of wear. The proprietary 3M cool flow valve is designed to release hot, humid exhaled breath quickly, helping to prevent an unpleasant build up of heat inside the facepiece a significant cause of discomfort to respirator wearers. The cool flow valves efficiency in keeping breathing cool and comfortable has been demonstrated through testing the atmosphere inside a respirator with a cool flow valve is on average 7.5°F cooler than the similar product without the valve. This makes cool flow valve respirators ideal for long periods of wear, especially where conditions are hot, humid or physically demanding. Testing conducted in a 3M laboratory.
Soft inner material provides added comfort while the cup shape design makes the respirator spacious and durable
M-noseclip adjusts easily for fewer pressure points and greater comfort
Braided headbands two-strap design with dual point attachment helps provide a secure seal

Product Name: 3M P100 Acid Gas and Organic Vapor Respirator Cartridge Replacement Pink 2 pc
Description:
The 3M Organic Vapor/Acid Gas Cartridge/Filter 60923 P100 helps provide protection against certain organic vapors, acid gases and particulates in a variety of environments. The cartridge/filter combination may be used for respiratory protection from certain organic vapors, chlorine, hydrogen chloride, sulfur dioxide, hydrogen sulfide, hydrogen fluoride and non-oil and oil particulate concentrations up to 10 times the Permissible Exposure Limit (PEL) with half facepieces or 50 times PEL with quantitatively fit tested full facepieces. This cartridge/filter is not for use in environments that are immediately dangerous to life or health (IDLH). Recommended applications for the cartridge/filter include chemical manufacturing, laboratories, petrochemical and pharmaceuticals. Inventory needs and training requirements for safety equipment are reduced because this respirator cartridge/filter selection works for many different applications. This cartridge/filter is commonly used in the following industries: chemicals, general manufacturing and pharmaceuticals. This organic vapor/acid gas cartridge/filter works with 3M Half and Full Facepieces 6000, 7000 and FF-400 Series with bayonet attachment holders. The cartridge is NIOSH (National Institute for Occupational Safety and Health) approved for environments containing acid gases and non-oil and oil particulates. The cartridge has been assigned the color code Magenta/Yellow in the NIOSH system. Breathing organic vapors, acid gases and particulates can pose a risk to your health. NIOSH a Federal government regulatory agency, has tested and approved the 3M Organic Vapor/Acid Gas Cartridge/Filter 60923 to help reduce exposure to certain organic vapors, acid gases and particulates.

Product Name: Milwaukee Anti-Scratch Safety Glasses Clear Lens Black/Red Frame
Description:
The Milwaukee Anti-Scratch Safety Glasses are designed for all day comfort with anti-scratch lenses. This protective eyewear has an anti-scratch hard coat to protect the lenses from the demands of the jobsite. The safety glasses feature comfortable temple arms designed for extended wear. These protective glasses have an integrated flexible nose bridge, providing you with extended comfort. These Milwaukee Anti-Scratch Safety Glasses are available with yellow, gray, clear and magnifying lenses. The yellow lenses make environments appear brighter, making them ideal for working in low light. Gray lenses are best for both indoor and outdoor work and magnifying lenses eliminate the need to wear additional eyewear under your safety glasses. Anti-Scratch Safety Glasses allow you to see what is important without sacrificing protection.
Third party tested and certified
Hard coat protects lenses

Clear lenses for enhanced contrast in low light applications
Lightweight and have a comfortable fit

Description:
The Milwaukee M12 Rivet Tool is the first cordless solution that offers fast, easy riveting while maintaining performance, durability, and size. The rivet gun can pull up to 25 3/16 in. stainless steel rivets or 45 in. steel rivets on one charge with a 1.5ah battery. The M12 cordless rivet tool offers 2X longer life over current cordless solutions and provides greater durability. The rivet gun is the most compact cordless rivet tool on the market at only 6.5 in. in length giving more access in tight spaces.

Description:
The Milwaukee M18 FUEL Compact Vacuum provides powerful performance and ultimate versatility to excel in small-area and spot clean-up applications on the jobsite. Armed with a Powerstate Brushless Motor and exclusive two-stage debris separation, the compact shop vac is optimized for dry jobsite debris. The two-stage debris separation divides small and large particles into the bagless canister prior to entering the filter. For maximum versatility, the portable vacuum's orientation and quick-change accessories can be manipulated from upright use at ground level, waist level or for use overhead.
50% more sustained suction vs. competition for more efficient clean-up
Maximum versatility: five dedicated accessory solutions
Redlink plus Intelligence: ensures optimal performance and maintains compatibility across the entire M18 System
Removeable canister for easy emptying of debris on or off tool
Quick-change accessories for upright use at ground level, waist level or overhead
On-board accessory holder provided for flexible hose, crevice tool, utility tool and brush tool

Product Name: Craftsman 20 gal Corded Wet/Dry Vacuum 12 amps 120 V 6.5 HP
Description:
The CRAFTSMAN 20 Gallon Wet/Dry Vac, featuring our most powerful 6.5 peak HP motor, is the ideal solution for tackling extra-large cleanups around the garage, shop and jobsite that need the most power and capacity.  This shop vacuum features on-board hose storage plus accessory and power cord organizers that help eliminate unneeded hassle and reduce overall storage space. Also included is a large 2-1/2-inch diameter vacuum hose with added Dual-Flex that resists kinks and crushing. For added versatility, the blowing port directs high speed exhaust air through the hose giving you the ability to go from cleaning up from a renovation to blasting yard waste from the deck.  Qwik Lock Filter Fastening System allows for quick and easy wet dry vacuum filter changes. This wet dry vac also comes equipped with an extra-large drain that quickly empties the tank of liquids. *Gallons indicated reflect drum volume, not necessarily collection capacity, actual capacity dependent upon type of debris collected, condition of filter and other factors. Product Name: DeWalt 20V MAX 5 amps Cordless Brushed 10 Tool Combo Kit
Description:
The DeWalt Combo Kit is ideal for almost any cutting, drilling or fastening applications. Improve productivity on the jobsite with innovative cordless solutions. 20V MAX tools are engineered to meet the specific needs of the most demanding trades. DCE100 has Max Air Flow of 100CFM. DCS393 20-volt max circular saw with 6-1/2 in, carbide blade can cut 2x4 ft. at a 45 angle in a single pass

Product Name: Milwaukee M18 FUEL 0920-20 9 gal Cordless Wet/Dry Vacuum Tool Only 18 V 4.25 HP
Description:
The Milwaukee M18 Fuel 9 Gallon Wet/Dry Vacuum brings unmatched performance, durability and versatility to jobsite cleanup. The PowerState Brushless Motor and optimized components Outperform 4.25 Peak HP Wet/Dry Vacuums, delivering more cleaning power than corded. The Dual-Battery Motor Head requires (2) M18 RedLithium Batteries to operate and cleans up more common Jobsite debris like drywall dust, concrete dust, and wood/metal shavings than 4.25 peak HP wet/dry vacuums in the same amount of time. This wet/dry vacuum provides the Most Durable Wheels and Hoses with reinforced casters and tread design for up to 8X wheel life and crush and twist-resistant hose for up to 2X hose life. This vac is part of the Most Versatile Wet/Dry Vacuum System with interchangeable motor heads, tanks and carts for varying performance, holding capacity and mobility with the easy access foot pedal.
Cart accessory storage allows for easy access to accessories when needed
Milwaukee fleece dust bags can be used for less debris build-up on the filter
Quickly swap or clean filters with the easy access quarter turn design
Delivers up to 49 minutes of continuous cleaning time and up to 1,600 ft. 2 of debris clean up per charge on a (2) HD12.0 battery packs
Delivers up to 34 minutes of continuous cleaning time and up to 1,400 ft. 2 of debris clean up per charge on (2) M18 RedLithium High Output HD12.0 battery packs

Description:
The Milwaukee M12 Air-Tip Utility Nozzle makes Jobsite cleanup easier with a powered brush roll that agitates debris for deep cleaning applications. The powered brush roll turns on at the push of a button and is powered by an M12 REDLITHIUM Battery. The Utility Nozzle will be able to clean up more debris in one pass for increased productivity. Description:
The EGO POWER+ 9 Gallon Wet/Dry Vacuum is the industry's most powerful cordless wet/dry vac with a brushless motor that delivers 110CFM of powerful suction for 100-inch lift. Plentiful onboard storage conveniently stows nozzles, extensions, and hose for easy organization of your shop vac accessories. A filter cleaning function keeps the filter clean for maximum suction and efficiency when filling its 9-gallon tank. It includes two extension tubes, a crevice nozzle, round brush dust nozzle, large floor nozzle and brush bar, rubber bar, compact floor nozzle, and a 1-7/8-inch hose. Product Name: Milwaukee M18 FUEL PACKOUT 0970-20 2.5 gal Cordless Wet/Dry Vacuum Tool Only 18 V
Description:
The Milwaukee M18 Fuel Packout 2.5 gallon wet/dry vacuum is the most powerful small capacity 18V wet/dry vacuum, fully compatible with all Milwaukee Packout modular storage system solutions. The Powerstate brushless motor delivers up to 60% more suction, giving users powerful performance to easily cleanup common wet and dry jobsite debris. Being Packout compatible gives this tool unmatched mobility, saving down time spent hauling tools on and off the site. At just 87 db(a), this vacuum is 2X quieter than traditional jobsite wet/dry vacuums. Users can use the vacuum on and off the Packout stack, making this the most portable and versatile wet/dry cleanup solution available. The vacuum comes with an included hepa filter for optimal dust and microparticle collection, as well as an included power tool adapter for efficient dust collection from other power tools. As a part of the M18 system of tools, it is powered by redlithium battery packs, which deliver up to 30 minutes of run time on a high output 8.0 battery pack in high mode and over 50+ minutes of run time in low mode.
47 in. water lift, powerful suction for wet and dry applications
Osha objective data compliance for select silica dust producing applications
Replacement washable certified Hepa filter
Built-in blower port
Fleece dust bag compatible

Product Name: Craftsman 16 gal Corded Wet/Dry Vacuum 12 amps 120 V 6.5 HP
Description:
The CRAFTSMAN 16 Gallon Wet/Dry Vac, featuring our most powerful 6.5 Peak HP motor, is the ideal solution for tackling large cleanup projects in the garage or on the jobsite that need the most power. Large scale renovations, builds, or floods are an easy task for this large shop vacuum.  This wet dry vac includes a car nozzle, utility nozzle and wet nozzle. Also included is a large 2-1/2 in. diameter hose with added Dual-Flex that resists kinks and crushing. On-board hose storage plus accessory and power cord organizers help eliminate unneeded hassle and reduce overall storage space. The Qwik Lock Filter Fastening System allows for quick and easy wet dry vacuum filter changes.  Equipped with an extra-large drain, the tank empties liquids quickly and easily. The blowing port directs high speed exhaust air through the hose giving you the ability to go from cleaning up from a renovation to blasting yard waste from the deck. *Gallons indicated reflect drum volume, not necessarily collection capacity, actual capacity dependent upon type of debris collected, condition of filter and other factors. Peak horsepower represents a level at or below the maximum horsepower output of an electric motor tested in a laboratory using a dynamometer.

DUAL-FLEX TECHNOLOGY: 2-1/2 in. diameter shop vacuum hose features Dual-Flex technology for 180-degree mobility at each end to resist kinking *

Description:
The 2 pack Red Stripe General Purpose Filter from CRAFTSMAN is designed to tackle everyday dirt like sawdust, jobsite debris and car or truck dirt. With up to 10 times the surface area of standard foam filters, the Red Stripe wet/dry vac filter is fully assembled and ready for use. The pleated paper technology creates an oversized surface area for efficient dust and dirt removal and can be easily cleaned. The Filter Fastening System makes removing and installing wet dry vacuum filters quick, easy and secure. To ensure maximum performance of your shop vacuum cleaner, replace wet/dry vac filters regularly.

Description:
The Milwaukee 15 pc. Sawzall Blade Kit with Packout Low Profile Compact Organizer includes a removable storage tray with the capacity to store up to 12-inch long Sawzall blades. Description:
The MILWAUKEE PACKOUT modular storage system is the industry's most durable and versatile storage system. The durable PACKOUT organizer is constructed with impact resistant materials. An IP65 rated weather seal protects tools, accessories, and small parts from rain and other jobsite debris. The organizer's interior has 10 removable storage bins that are mountable for quick access. Product Name: Weed Dragon Weed Torch Kit 1 pc Propane
Description:
The Weed Dragon is the perfect propane torch kit for home and garden use. We've regulated the flame and BTU down for homeowners who don't need the power of a farm torch and we've even assembled it. This torch kit is still plenty powerful for lots of tough jobs all year long and generates heat up to 2,000 degree F. The 100,000 BTU Weed Dragon quickly hooks up to any refillable propane tank (barbeque cylinders work great) and even comes with a hand-tighten tank fitting (you don't even need a wrench). This weed dragon 100,000 BTU unit is a complete torch kit with needle adjusting valve. Torch kit comes fully assembled with a 2 in. bell, 23 in. steel handle painted green, 10ft. hose, pol fitting and needle turn valve.
A 20 lb or larger propane tank is the recommended fuel source.
CSA certified for the us and canada. Torch comes complete and no assembly is required.

Description:
Our Grinder Paddle Switch, No Lock is the next advancement in power and performance, generating 11A corded power, fastest cutting. and delivering up to 135 cuts per charge. The Grinder generates power allowing you to complete the toughest grinding and cutting applications, all on the M18 Cordless System. The Power state Brushless Motor delivers maximum sustained power and 8,500 RPM to remove material faster and increase productivity. Red link Plus Intelligence ensures unmatched levels of performance, protection, and compatibility. The M18 Red lithium High Output XC6.0 Batteries (not included) deliver 50 percent more power while running 50 percent cooler than our M18 Red lithium XC Batteries and are compatible with 200+ Tools in the M18 System. With tool-free accessory and guard adjustments, you will experience faster accessory changes and less downtime, while remaining fully compatible with the most common accessories in the market. The Grinder takes cordless grinders to the next level in performance and run-time.

Product Name: Milwaukee 18V M18 Cordless Multi-Tool Kit (Battery)
Description:
The Milwaukee M18 Cordless Multi-Tool cuts up to 50 percent faster and gives you up to 2X more cuts per charge than competitors. The oscillating multi-tool features best-in-class speed and performance and gives you the versatility to complete problematic job site applications. The cordless multi-tool is ideal for remodelers, flooring contractors, maintenance repair technicians, and electricians. The battery-powered multi-tool is powered by the M18 Redlithium Battery giving you up to 40 percent more run-time. It gives you the power to grind, sand, and scrape at odd angles and in areas difficult to work. It also allows you to make flush or plunge cuts, remove grout in corners and tackle other awkward jobs. The tool's Constant Power Technology maintains blade speed for faster cutting during heavy applications. A 12-setting dial allows you to match the speed to the application. It includes five assorted sanding sheets, a sanding pad, and a wood cutting blade.

Product Name: Milwaukee 18V M18 Redlithium Forge Pack 6 Ah Lithium-Ion Rechargeable Battery Pack 2 pc
Description:
The Milwaukee M18 Redlithium forge XC6.0 battery pack delivers high output 12.0 power in a smaller size, a 15 minute supercharge of up to 80 percent, and the longest life vs Redlithium batteries. Redlithium forge are Milwaukee's most powerful, fastest charging, and longest life batteries. The Redlithium forge XC6.0 delivers the same power as the M18 Redlithium high output HD12.0 in a smaller size and lighter weight design. The optimized combination of size, weight, and increased power provides the best solution for power demanding overhead work and tight work areas. The Redlithium forge XC6.0 is the fastest charging battery pack within its class on M18, charging in just 15 minutes to 80 percent with the new M18 Dual bay simultaneous super Charger. This lithium ion battery has the longest life, the most recharges, and the best performance over the life of the battery. This solution is designed with resistant housing for increased protection against exposure to common oils, greases, and solvents. Built in Redlink Intelligence protects the battery from overloads, preventing you from damaging your cordless power tools in heavy-duty situations. The Redlithium forge XC6.0 battery is fully compatible with 250+ M18 solutions.

Product Name: Milwaukee PACKOUT 22 in. Rolling Modular Tool Box Black/Red
Description:
Packout modular storage system is the industry's most durable and versatile storage system. The Packout rolling tool box is constructed with impact resistant polymers and metal reinforced corners so it can withstand harsh jobsite environments. The rolling tool storage box connects with all other Packout system components via integrated locking cleats and features a 250 lbs of weight capacity. An industrial-grade extension handle and 9" all-terrain wheels ensure you can roll the tool box anywhere on the jobsite. An IP65 rated weather seal protects your tools and accessories from rain and other jobsite debris. Interior organizer trays allow you to keep equipment organized to fit your needs. Reinforced hinges and carry handle ensure the rolling tool box is easily transportable wherever you need it. Packout modular storage allows you to customize and build your own storage system to easily transport and organize your tools and accessories. To build out your own custom PACKOUT Stack, visit this link on the ACE Hardware Website: https://www.acehardware.com/packout-builder

Product Name: Milwaukee MX FUEL Carry-On Lithium-Ion 3600W/1800W Power Supply Power Supply with Battery
Description:
The Milwaukee MX Fuel Carry-on 3600W/1800W Power Supply provides the best temporary power for the job. You can power more on-demand with efficient, quiet, and portable power anywhere. The portable power supply offers 3600 peak watts, and 1800 continuous watts of pure sine inverter energy, powering everything from your high demand 15A tools to sensitive electronics. The compact size, no emissions, and quiet operation of the power supply unit allow you to use it safely in confined spaces indoors. The metal roll cage provides you with durability for outdoor jobsite use. The battery-powered generator eliminates the cost of gasoline and doesn't require engine repair or maintenance, reducing your downtime and allowing you to get jobs done faster. The cordless generator can be powered by a single battery for lightweight portability or two batteries for double the run time. The MX Fuel Redlithium Forge HD12.0 battery pack delivers up to 2x more runtime, has Cool-Cycle capability for high-speed cooling while charging, and the longest life versus Redlithium batteries. Redlithium Forge is Milwaukee's most powerful, fastest charging, and longest-life battery. With 2X more runtime vs MX Fuel Redlithium XC406 (XC6.0), this battery delivers more work per charge allowing you to run your equipment longer and keep up with high-demand applications.

Product Name: Milwaukee M18 Cordless Oscillating Multi-Tool Kit (Battery & Charger)
Description:
The Milwaukee M18 Cordless Multi-Tool cuts up to 50 percentage faster and gives you up to 2X more cuts per charge than competitors. The oscillating multi-tool features best-in-class speed and performance and gives you the versatility to complete problematic job site applications. The cordless multi-tool is ideal for remodelers, flooring contractors, maintenance repair technicians, and electricians. The battery-powered multi-tool is powered by the M18 Redlithium Battery giving you up to 40 percentage more run-time. It gives you the power to grind, sand, and scrape at odd angles and in areas difficult to work. It also allows you to make flush or plunge cuts, remove grout in corners and tackle other awkward jobs. The tool's Constant Power Technology maintains blade speed for faster cutting during heavy applications. A 12-setting dial allows you to match the speed to the application. It includes 5 assorted sanding sheets, a sanding pad, and a wood cutting blade.

Product Name: Milwaukee M18 RedLithium Forge 8 Ah Lithium-Ion XC8.0 Battery Pack
Description:
The M18 RedLithium FORGE XC8.0 Battery Pack delivers High Output 12.0 power in a smaller size, high-speed cooling for less downtime in high-demand applications. Has a  35-minute supercharge to 80%, and the longest life vs RedLithium batteries. RedLithium Forge are Milwaukee's most powerful, fastest charging, and longest-life batteries. The M18 RedLithium Forge XC 8.0 delivers 8 amp hours of runtime with the same power as the M18 RedLithium High Output HD12.0, in a smaller size and lighter weight design. The M18 RedLithium Forge XC8.0 is Cool-Cycle capable. Cool-Cycle Active Cooling System provides high-speed cooling for less downtime. Patented ingress coating provides increased protection to maximize active cooling through an upgraded venting design. The high-speed cooling feature works with M18 chargers that have COOL-CYCLE capability. When paired with the M18 Dual Bay Simultaneous Super Charger, this battery charges in just 35 minutes to 80%, getting you back to work faster than ever before. This lithium-ion battery has the longest life, the most recharges, and the best performance over the life of the battery. It is also designed with resistant housing for increased protection against exposure to common oils, greases, and solvents. Redlink Intelligence protects the battery from overloads, preventing you from damaging your cordless power tools in heavy-duty situations. The M18 RedLithium Forge   XC 8.0 battery is fully compatible with 250+ M18 solutions.
Built to withstand the rigors of professional use, this battery is constructed with durable materials and features robust housing to endure impacts and harsh working environments, ensuring long-term reliability
Designed for efficiency, it supports rapid charging, allowing you to quickly recharge the battery between tasks, reducing idle time and maximizing productivity on the job site
Despite its high capacity, the Milwaukee M18 RedLithium Forge battery remains compact and lightweight, facilitating comfortable handling and reducing user fatigue during prolonged use
Incorporating overload protection mechanisms, the battery safeguards against overheating, overloading, and over-discharging, prolonging its lifespan and ensuring safe operation

Product Name: Milwaukee M18 Forge 6 Ah Lithium-Ion Battery and Charger 2 pc
Description:
The Milwaukee M18 Redlithium Forge XC6.0 battery pack with M18 dual-bay simultaneous supercharger starter kit. Delivers high output 12.0 power in a smaller size, 15-minute supercharge up to 80 percent , and the longest life vs Redlithium batteries. Redlithium Forge is Milwaukee's most powerful, fastest charging, and longest-life battery. The Redlithum forge XC6.0 delivers the same power as the M18 Redlithium high output hd12.0 in a smaller size and lighter weight design. The optimized combination of size, weight, and increased power provides the best solution for power-demanding overhead work and tight work areas. The Redlithium Forge XC6.0 is the fastest charging battery pack within its class on M18, charging in just 15 minutes to 80 percent with the new M18 dual-bay simultaneous supercharger. This lithium-ion battery has the longest life, the most recharges, and best performance over the life of the battery. This solution is designed with resistant housing for increased protection against exposure to common oils, greases, and solvents. Built-in redlink intelligence protects the battery from overloads, preventing you from damaging your cordless power tools in heavy-duty situations. The Redlithium Forge XC6.0 battery is fully compatible with 250+ M18 solutions.
Adaptive charge distribution delivers adaptive simultaneous charging for multiple batteries to maximize productivity
Active cooling system provides instant cooling for less downtime
Active cooling feature works with batteries that have cool-cycle capability

Product Name: Milwaukee M18 FUEL 1/2 in. Brushless Cordless Hammer Drill/Drive Kit (Battery & Charger)
Description:
The Milwaukee M18 Fuel 1/2 in. hammer drill driver is the industry's most powerful hammer drill, delivering the capability to drill the largest holes at high speed into the densest materials. The cordless drill is the most compact solution in its class and features an autostop control mode for enhanced safety. The Powerstate brushless motor delivers the most power under load to complete 2-9/16 in. self-feed holes in dense woods for increased productivity. At only 6.9in length, this is the most compact cordless drill in its class for the best access and maneuverability in tight spaces. The Autostop control mode offers enhanced safety for the operator by preventing over-rotation in a bind-up with the best reaction time in the industry. The Redlink Plus intelligence ensures maximum performance and protects from overloads, heating, and over-discharge. The Milwaukee Redlithium XC5.0 battery pack delivers more work per charge and more work over the life of the pack when compared to competitors.

Product Name: Milwaukee M12 FUEL 3 in. Cordless Brushless Compact Cut-Off Tool Tool Only
Description:
The M12 Fuel 3 in. Compact Cut-Off Tool delivers multi-material cutting capability in an ergonomic package, optimized for one-handed use. Spinning at 20,000 rpm and featuring a Powerstate Brushless Motor, 2522 delivers fast and accurate cutting performance in a wide range of materials. Lastly, the tool features tool-free guard adjustment and an LED light.

Product Name: Milwaukee M18 FUEL 1/2 in. High Torque Impact Wrench and Grease Gun Kit (Battery & Charger)
Category: High Torque Impact Wrench and Grease Gun
Description:
The MILWAUKEE M18 FUEL ½ in. HTIW w/ Friction Ring & Grease Gun Combo Kit includes the most power-dense impact wrench in its class, provides greater access in tight spaces, and maximizes productivity through faster removal speeds. The POWERSTATE Brushless Motor delivers up to 1,100 ft-lbs. of fastening Torque and 1,500 ft-lbs. of Nut-Busting Torque when paired with our M18 REDLITHIUM XC5.0 Battery, while the compact size at 7.6 in. in length gives users greater access in tight spaces. The M18 FUEL ½ in. High Torque Impact Wrench w/ Friction Ring maximizes productivity on the jobsite and in the shop by removing stubborn bolts and fasteners faster than cordless competitors. Our patented battery isolation system provides a secure battery connection and controls vibration transmitted to the pack. Tri-LEDs surround the anvil to deliver brighter light with fewer shadows. 4-Mode DRIVE CONTROL offers greater precision with a range of pre-set RPM and IPM levels, selectable from a single button on the tool. By selecting Mode 4, AUTO SHUT-OFF control applies no more than 50 ft-lbs. of torque for hand-tight fastening applications to prevent overtightening. Mode 4 also features bolt removal control that delivers our users full torque output, then decreases RPMs once the bolt is loosened to prevent fastener drops. The ½ in. friction ring design allows for quick & tool-free socket changes. The included battery provides increased protection against oils, greases, & solvents.

Product Name: Dremel 12V B815-01 2 amps Lithium-Ion Battery 1 pk
Description:
In a world full of knock-offs & duplicates, all batteries are not created equally. Dremel batteries are built for Dremel tools. Outstanding performance starts with power through the B815-01 12V 2Ah battery. At 2Ah, the B815-01 12V battery provides 2 amps of current per hour of use, giving your Dremel tool the life it needs to complete your tasks. Including 3 state-of-the-art cells in the B815-01 12V battery, the power output gives you the strength needed to cut, carve, sand, engrave, and more. This battery fits seamlessly with Dremel 8240, 8250 & 8260 models. Driven by technology, the B815-01 is built to protect against overheating, overload and unnecessary discharge for ultimate project efficiency. Lastly, having additional batteries can keep your project moving...use one while you charge the other...to help you complete your task without unnecessary stoppage or downtime.
2Ah (amp-hour) capacity keeps your cordless rotary tool charged up and ready to go
For use with Dremel 12V MAX Lithium-Ion cordless tools 8200, 8220 and 8300
Compact and durable

Our M12 fuel hatchet 6 in. pruning saw kit delivers unmatched control and access, has the power to cut 3 in. hardwoods and delivers up to 120 cuts per charge. The M12 red lithium XC 4.0Ah battery delivers best-in-class run-time and performance. This pruning saw features a full house chain, easy access chain tensioner, automatic oiler, metal bucking spikes and onboard storage for the scrench. The Milwaukee M12 fuel hatchet 6 in. The pruning saw is part of the M12 system which is fully compatible with over 100 solutions.

Product Name: Diablo 5 in. Ceramic Blend Hook and Lock Sanding Disc 40 Grit Ultra Coarse 50 pk
Description:
Diablo's premium 5 in. 40-Grit universal random orbital sanding (ROS) discs with Hook & Lock backing include break-through innovations that improve performance, extend sanding life and increase productivity. Featuring a premium ceramic blend, these discs remove material faster than other sanding discs and offer an extra long sanding life. Clog-Shield, Diablo's own blend of grinding agents, reduces loading thus maximizing productivity. The superior grain bonding system, Endura-Bond, provides Diablo's sanding discs with longer life and extreme durability.
Universal hole pattern, a one-size-fits-all design (fits all 5 and 8-hole sanders) for fast and precise alignment
Premium ceramic grain blend, a superior quality formulation designed for fast material removal and long sanding life
Premium hook and lock backing enables repeated attachment and removal of discs for a consistent secure connection
Clog-Shield, a proprietary blend of grinding agents that reduce pitch build-up and clogging
For orbital and DA sanders in wood, metal and plastics
Ideal for fast leveling, shaping, extra heavy removal and stripping

Product Name: Milwaukee M18 FUEL 2727-21HD 16 in. 18 V Battery Chainsaw Kit (Battery & Charger)
Description:
The Milwaukee M18 fuel 16 in. chainsaw delivers the power to cut hardwoods, cuts faster than gas and delivers up to 150 cuts per charge. The unit is designed to meet the performance, durability and ergonomic needs of professional landscape maintenance, power utility and the installed M18 user. The Power state brushless motor maintains speed under heavy loads without bogging down to outperform small gas engines and higher voltage systems. Redlink Plus intelligence ensures maximum performance and protection from overload, overheating and over-discharge. The M18 Red lithium High Output HD12.0 battery delivers unmatched run-time in all applications. M18 fuel technology allows the unit to reach full throttle in under 1 second providing ultimate control and productivity.
Same power and performance as a 40 cc gas chainsaw
Automatic oiler for proper chain lubrication and increased productivity, variable speed trigger for full control
Dual-stud for improved bar and chain retention
Onboard storage for scratch
Redlink plus intelligence ensures optimal performance and provides overload protection to prevent damage to the tool and battery during heavy applications while still maintaining compatibility across the entire M18 system
Purposely built for the M18 fuel 16 in. chainsaw to provide the power and performance of a gas engine up to 40CC
Redlithium high output HD12.0 battery pack provides 50 percent more power and runs 50 percent cooler versus standard redlithium HD packs
Superior pack construction provides the industry's best protection against jobsite conditions

Diablo's new reusable hand sanding block maximizes sanding performance by enabling professional users to sand flat and contour surfaces with one tool. This premium foam tool includes two sides: cushioned for controlled material removal in contour sanding and dense for aggressive material removal on flat surfaces. Hook Lock backing allows repeated attachment and removal of Diablo SandNet sheets. Included with the Reusable Hand Sanding Block are five SandNet sheets, ranging from coarse/removal to ultra-fine finish. The reusable SandNet nylon design is easy to clean and reuse multiple times, simply shake, vacuum or rinse to remove any build up.

Product Name: Diablo Steel Demon 7-1/4 in. D X 5/8 in. Cermet Metal Saw Blade 48 teeth 1 pk
Description:
Diablo's new steel demon cermet saw blade series is redefining metal cutting and the jobsite, by introducing safer, exclusive innovation that allows users to cut both mild and stainless steels for 40X longer life versus standard carbide-tipped metal cutting saw blades. The specially formulated cermet (Ceramic and Metallic) teeth provide high heat tolerances and increased hardness for superior wear and ultimate cutting life. Featuring a special triple chip grind and perma-shield coating, these blades slice through the toughest of metals to produce precise cuts with less sparks and burr-free finishes that require no rework. The ability to cut through both mild and stainless steel eliminates the need for individually dedicated saw blades, offering a one-blade solution for ultimate metal cutting performance and unmatched value story, forever changing the metal cutting industry.
Laser Cut Arbor reduces vibration and premature wear for accurate blade rotation when in use
Laser cut arbor reduces vibration and premature wear for accurate blade rotation when in use on the saw
Up to 50X cooler cuts with a circular saw blade when compared to a grinding disc that increases temperature of steel by up to 500 degrees. Grinding discs increase the temperature enough to permanently discolor the steel.
Up to 10X faster cuts with a circular saw blade for maximum productivity and efficiency, resulting in up to 60 seconds faster cuts in both metals and stainless steels versus standard grinding discs
Triple Chip Cutting action reduces sparks and the possibility of needing hot permits
Optimized blade design reduces wandering and deflection of metal, creating precise cuts that require virtually no re-work
Advanced Laser Cut Stabilizer Vents trap noise and vibration for maximum stability, keeping the blade cool for straight, accurate cuts
Tri-Metal Shock Resistant Brazing, a three-metal brazing system, allows Cermet II teeth to withstand extreme impact for maximum durability
Laser Cut Thin Kerf Design provides less resistance and heat build-up for ease of cut, accuracy and long cutting life in cordless or corded saws
Perma-SHIELD coating resists heat build-up by protecting the blade against gumming and corrosion

Our Milwaukee 25 ft. Compact Wide Blade Magnetic Tape Measure with Rechargeable 100 lm Light provides the brightest and clearest measuring in the industry. Product Name: Blaze Laser Measure 100 ft. Black/Blue 1 pc
Description:
This Blaze 100 ft. laser measure is a fully featured tool with a brighter graphic display and a new user-interface design for easier measuring. The user-friendly layout features a two-button operation: one for measuring, and one for rounding. The rounding button is a unique function that allows the user to easily round the measurement result from 1/2 in. up to 1/32 in. It has the default real-time measurement mode, immediately providing accurate measurement that automatically adjusts closer to or farther from the target. The laser measure features an enhanced user interface, including a click wheel for easy setting and function navigation. Its keypad design includes a standalone recessed measuring button, to make it easy to distinguish just by feel. It features full rubber over mold housing, which helps protect every major point, with a design similar to a roll cage.
This compact measurer is easy to carry and fits in your pocket
Illuminates numbers with distinct resolution, for work in low-light conditions and better readability
Includes intuitive icons, big-number mode and upgraded contrast to make it easier to read
The grip is slimmer, making the laser easier to handle

Product Name: Bosch 2.1 in. L X 1.2 in. W Laser Measure 165 ft. Black/Blue 1 pc
Description:
This 165 ft. laser measure is a fully-featured tool with an easy-to-read color display, great accuracy and reinforced housing for durability. The Bosch Blaze has accuracy up to1/16 in. plus it includes a rounding button that rounds the measurement to the fraction that best suits the application and haptic feedback for loud jobsites. The digital laser measure also offers full rubber over-mold housing, designed to be similar to a roll cage. It is IP65 rated and has an ergonomic design for better grip. It has a default real-time measurement mode, which immediately provides accurate measuring that automatically adjusts closer to or farther from the target. It includes 11 different measuring functions, including real-time length, length, area, volume, indirect functions and addition/subtraction capability.
Belt clip - allows convenient storage on jobsite

Product Name: Milwaukee 4.2 in. L X 1.9 in. W Laser Distance Meter 150 ft. Black/Red 1 pc
Description:
The MILWAUKEE 150 Laser Distance Meters are designed to provide the easiest measurements from all orientations, and feature an array of new functionalities. Each laser distance meter offers several different measurement functions, including add and subtract values and calculate linear distance, surface area, total area, and volume. The laser distance meters have simple user interfaces for fast navigation to quickly choose a function and take a measurement with minimal downtime. The 2 distance meter screen offers maximum visibility in low light conditions. The 150 laser distance meter includes a built-in two-position auto-detecting lever to easily measure in corners. The distance meters include memory storage for up to 30 readings and an impact-resistant over mold for protection from tough jobsite conditions. The laser distance meters also feature a side shot button for an easier, more ergonomic experience when measuring in all directions.
2 position auto-detecting lever
Continuous real-time measurements

Backlit color screen

 +/- 1/16 inch accuracy

Product Name: C.H. Hanson 1000 ft. L X 3 in. W Plastic Caution Barricade Tape Yellow
Description:
C.H. Hanson's heavy-duty barricade tape is an excellent choice for marking dangerous, construction, or hazardous areas. Choose from pre-printed messages to aid in alerting passers-by, block off restricted areas, or obstructing dangerous paths. This strong tape is constructed from weatherproof poly vinyl chloride that is designed with toughness to hold up to harsh outdoor conditions. Our non-adhesive, non-conductive vinyl barricade tape has added plasticizers for increased elasticity. Fade resistant colors quickly catch people's eyes and alerts them of the danger or caution that must be taken. Adding to the alert, our message is printed on the tape in large, bold 2 inch black capital letters, repeating all the way through.

Product Name: Crescent Wiss 9-3/4 in. Stainless Steel Straight Combination Pattern Snips 18 Ga. 1 pk
Description:
Crescent Wiss has taken the Aviation Snip to the next level with the advanced MetalMaster Aviation Snips.  The precision-cast molybdenum blades have CNC-ground serrations which allow for more uniform serrations that provide a cleaner cut every time. They are available in left/straight cut, right/straight cut, and straight cut.

Product Name: Craftsman 6 gal Corded Wet/Dry Vacuum 7.5 amps 120 V 3.5 HP
Description:
The CRAFTSMAN 6 Gallon Wet/Dry Vac, featuring a 3.5 peak HP motor, is a great lightweight and small capacity vac for the home and garage. It's a great match for cleanups ranging from draining flooded dishwashers, to cleaning out a vehicle, boat or RV, to picking up broken glass, dirt or debris from a home renovation.  This wet dry vacuum easily stores away with its compact size and on-board hose, accessory and power cord organizers that reduce overall storage space. Swivel casters let you get around easily, while the rear wheels keep the vac upright on rough surfaces.  This 6 gallon shop vacuum also features on-board hose storage plus accessory and power cord organizers that help eliminate unneeded hassle and reduce overall storage space. The Qwik Lock Filter Fastening System makes removing and installing wet dry vacuum filters quick, easy and secure. *Gallons indicated reflect drum volume, not necessarily collection capacity, actual capacity dependent upon type of debris collected, condition of filter and other factors. Peak horsepower represents a level at or below the maximum horsepower output of an electric motor tested in a laboratory using a dynamometer.

Product Name: Craftsman 4 gal Corded Wet/Dry Vacuum 120 V 5 HP
Description:
Perfect for auto-detailing, small project cleaning, home cleaning and home repair restoration,  the CRAFTSMAN 4 Gallon Wet/Dry Vac is a great fit for your home or DIY projects. Small, but mighty, this 4 gallon vacuum has a 5.0 peak HP motor and is lightweight, making it a portable, powerful solution for your cleanup needs. The built-in storage system keeps all five accessories together in one convenient place. The 15-foot cord 7-foot hose gives you space to move around the room, while the large top handle provides grip while cleaning. This shop vac features a large on/off switch making it easy for you to control the power when needed. The CRAFTSMAN 4 Gallon Wet/Dry Vac also comes with 5 accessories to help you do the job: 2 extension wands, a car nozzle, a utility tool, and a dusting brush. Extension wands can be used for hard-to-reach places, such as in between or  under car seats, corners of trunks or hatches, or along newly installed framework. The car nozzle is designed to deep clean car fabrics such as your seat as well as your car mats. The utility tool is a multipurpose attachment for easy or debris pickup on floors and other surfaces. Whether it's cleaning your kids' playroom, your mud room, or cleaning up your work bench, the CRAFTSMAN 4 Gallon Wet/Dry Vacuum is perfect for your everyday needs. For delicate surfaces, make sure to add the CRAFTSMAN Natural Hair Brush Dusting Brush (CMXYZVBE38785; sold separately) to your shop vacuum for cleaning spaces like your car seats or car dashboards. Outside of your car, the Natural Hair Brush Dusting Brush is perfect for wood surfaces. For easy cleanup, make sure you have the Craftsman dust bag (CMXYZVBE43271; sold separately) on hand. Gallons indicated reflect drum volume, not necessarily collection capacity, actual capacity dependent upon type of debris collected, condition of filter and other factors. Product Name: Craftsman 12 gal Corded Wet/Dry Vacuum 10.5 amps 120 V 6 HP
Description:
The CRAFTSMAN 12 Gallon Wet/Dry Vac, featuring a powerful 6.0 peak HP motor, is our most compact high performance vac, great for tackling medium to large cleanup projects in the garage, shop and on the jobsite. This vac can handle any mess and gives the homeowner, garage dweller or home renovator a solid capacity for tough messes. This 12-gallon shop vacuum is equipped with a large 2-1/2-inch diameter hose that allows for larger pickups and features Dual-Flex that adds flexibility at each end. On-board hose storage plus accessory and power cord organizers help eliminate unneeded hassle and reduce overall storage space. The Qwik Lock Filter Fastening System allows for quick and easy wet dry vacuum filter changes. Equipped with an extra-large drain, it quickly empties the tank of liquids. *Gallons indicated reflect drum volume, not necessarily collection capacity, actual capacity dependent upon type of debris collected, condition of filter and other factors. Peak horsepower represents a level at or below the maximum horsepower output of an electric motor tested in a laboratory using a dynamometer.

BUILT-IN BLOWER PORT: Rear blowing port on this wet dry vac allows for quick cleaning of leaves and grass clippings in your garage and outdoors
EXTRA-LONG POWER CORD: 20-foot power cord provides reach for most chores and wraps neatly around ergonomic, carry handle for storage

Product Name: Craftsman Versastack 1/4, 3/8 and 1/2 in. drive Metric and SAE Mechanic's Tool Set 230 pc
Description:
The CMMT45305 230 PC. Versastack 3-Drawer Mechanics toolset is fully compatible and can be stacked on or under other Versastack components. The Craftsman Versastack system is a flexible platform that allows for many different combinations of storage solutions based on the user needs. Featuring an easy use drawer lock dial, drawers lock in place when not in use to prevent contents from falling out. Drawers open with one hand and can nest on top of the box for easy access and temporary storage. Made to tackle any task, this set is filled with an assortment of 230 mechanics tools. Product Name: Craftsman V20 CMCK279C2 10 in. 20 V Battery Blower/Trimmer Kit (Battery & Charger)
Description:
Everything you need for trimming and clean up and then some. The V20 Weedwacker String Trimmer and Blower Combo Kit comes equipped with two (2) 1.5 Ah batteries, along with powerful lightweight motors that offer the convenience and efficiency to make you look forward to yard day. The Automatic Feed System lets you keep your pace without needing to stop and bump the trimmer to extend the line. The Blower delivers up to 200 CFM and up to 90 MPH of air flow designed to rid the most stubborn yard waste and finish the job post-trim or take on more outdoor cleanup tasks. Once the task is finished, conveniently store your tool using the integrated VersaTrack hook with the VersaTrack system. The V20 battery platform is compatible with Craftsman V20 Outdoor Equipment and Power Tools. You'll find the complete line of outdoor tools and equipment essentials for a job to make you proud.
Automatic feed spool extends 0.065 in. trimmer line without user assistance
Edge guide designed to cut work time and increase trim accuracy

Product Name: Craftsman 9 gal Corded Wet/Dry Vacuum 8.3 amps 120 V 4.25 HP
Description:
The CRAFTSMAN 9 Gallon Wet/Dry Vac, featuring a 4.25 peak HP motor, is great for home renovations or home emergencies. Equipped with one of the most powerful motors our compact vacs have to offer, the 9-gallon shop vacuum is great for general garage cleaning, basement cleanup from flooding or seepage, as well as, removing water from clogged sinks. With an extra-large drain, liquids can be emptied quickly and easily from the tank. The Qwik Lock Filter Fastening System allows for quick and easy wet dry vacuum filter changes. Store this wet dry vac with ease. On-board hose storage, plus accessory and power cord organizers help eliminate unneeded hassle and reduce overall storage space. *Gallons indicated reflect drum volume, not necessarily collection capacity, actual capacity dependent upon type of debris collected, condition of filter and other factors. Peak horsepower represents a level at or below the maximum horsepower output of an electric motor tested in a laboratory using a dynamometer.

Product Name: Milwaukee M18 FUEL 18 Volt Brushless 30 deg Framing Nailer Kit
Description:
The Milwaukee M18 Fuel 30 degree framing Nailer Kit sets the new standard for cordless framing nailers. It has a nitrogen spring mechanism, Powerstate brushless motor, and Redlink Intelligence, providing pneumatic performance and cordless convenience. The framing nailer can sink full round head nails into dense engineered lumber to tackle the most demanding framing applications. To increase productivity and efficiency, the framing gun fires 3 nails per second with zero ramp-up time, firing a nail as soon as the trigger is pulled. The cordless framing nailer uses only Milwaukee's Redlithium batteries and sealed compressed nitrogen to drive each nail. The M18 Fuel 30 degree framing nailer delivers pneumatic performance and durability that professional carpenters and remodelers expect, without the hassle of a compressor and hose or gas cartridge.
Power to sink nails in engineered lumber
No gas cartridge required - completely battery operated
Sequential and contact actuation firing modes
Tool free drive depth adjustment
No-mark tip cover - ensure the nails are driven securely without causing any damage to the surrounding material
Dry fire lockout - prevents accidental firing without nails loaded

It comes equipped with an 8 in. bar and chain and features a high-efficiency brushless motor that delivers up to 96 cuts per charge. It also features metal bucking strips for a durable cutting grip and a tree hook allows you to easily remove pruned branches.

Product Name: DeWalt 60V MAX Flexvolt 12 in. Cordless Brushless Dual-Bevel Sliding Compound Miter Saw Tool Only
Description:
Easily tackle demanding woodworking applications with the 60V MAX 12in. Double Bevel Sliding Miter Saw. Cut. Capture. Charge with Regenerative Braking Technology to extend runtime with virtually every cut, up to 675 cuts in 3-1/4 in. MDF base molding or up to 255 cuts in pressure-treated 4 in. x 4 in. timber, all on only one DeWalt Flexvolt DCB609 battery. This miter saw features an efficient bevel gear transmission and can capture up to 94% of dust. The Cutline blade positioning system provides accurate cut-line indication. The saw also features updated controls designed for overall ergonomics compared to previous DeWalt designs. At a weight of 50.9 lb (tool only), easily take this saw on the go across demanding jobsites.
Easy to use - easy blade change and cut depth, miter and bevel cut adjustment
Single battery operation capable power from 60V MAX to tackle professional applications
Exceptional runtime delivers up to 675 cuts in 3-1/4 in. MDF base molding & 255 cuts in pressure treated 4 in. x 4 in. lumber
Regenerative Braking technology extends runtime by redirecting lost energy back into the battery (sold separately)
Efficient dust capture up to 94% of dust captured when cutting 2x10 SPF using DWV015 dust extractor (sold separately)

Product Name: Milwaukee M18 FUEL 16 Ga. 18 Volt Brushless 20 deg Angled Finish Nailer Kit
Description:
The Milwaukee M18 Fuel 16 gauge angled finish nailer kit provides peak productivity on the jobsite, delivering unmatched nailing performance without the hassle of a compressor and hose. Leveraging a nitrogen air spring mechanism, this cordless 16 gauge finish nailer allows users to consistently sink nails to their required depth in hard and soft woods while leaving clean nail holes, making for repeatable results and easy filling. The nitrogen air spring mechanism, combined with Milwaukee Powerstate brushless motor and Redlink plus Intelligence, delivers a pneumatic-like nailing response with zero ramp-up time from nail to nail, keeping users productive and efficient throughout their job. This Milwaukee cordless finish nailer features a compact and ergonomic design providing access into tight spaces where nailing is required while limiting fatigue when using the tool. The M18 Fuel 16 gauge angled finish nailer kit delivers the pneumatic performance that professional carpenters and remodelers demand with finishing nails for trim, crown molding, baseboards, and more in tight spaces with the freedom and convenience of cordless.
Tool free jam clearing latch and depth adjustment
Sequential and contact actuation firing modes
Reversible belt hook - clip the nailer either to the right or left side of your belt, depending on your personal preference
Built in LED light - Illuminates work surfaces in dark location
Fires 800 nails per charge on M18 CP2.0 battery

Product Name: Milwaukee M18 FUEL 16 Ga. 18 Volt Brushless 20 deg Angled Finish Nailer
Description:
The Milwaukee M18 Fuel 16 gauge angled finish nailer provides peak productivity on the jobsite, delivering unmatched nailing performance without the hassle of a compressor and hose. Leveraging a nitrogen air spring mechanism, this cordless 16 gauge finish nailer allows users to consistently sink nails to their required depth in hard and soft woods while leaving clean nail holes, making for repeatable results and easy filling. The nitrogen air spring mechanism, combined with Milwaukee Powerstate brushless motor and Redlink plus Intelligence, delivers a pneumatic-like nailing response with zero ramp-up time from nail to nail, keeping users productive and efficient throughout their job. This Milwaukee cordless finish nailer features a compact and ergonomic design providing access into tight spaces where nailing is required while limiting fatigue when using the tool. When paired with an M18 Redlithium CP2.0 battery pack, this finish nail gun fires up to 800 nails per charge and is fully compatible with all M18 Redlithium batteries. The M18 Fuel 16 gauge angled finish nailer delivers the pneumatic performance that professional carpenters and remodelers demand with finishing nails for trim, crown molding, baseboards, and more in tight spaces with the freedom and convenience of cordless.
Tool free jam clearing latch and depth adjustment
Sequential and contact actuation firing modes
Reversible belt hook - clip the nailer either to the right or left side of your belt, depending on your personal preference
Built in LED light - Illuminates work surfaces in dark location

Product Name: Milwaukee M12 Cable Stapler
Description:
The Milwaukee M12 cable stapler delivers unmatched stapling performance in the most compact battery-powered solution leading to a faster, more efficient rough-in process. Our compact, lightweight design provides users with access to tight stud bays and improved ergonomics when stapling overhead or during difficult-to-reach situations. Moveable cable guides ensure proper alignment and the coil-spring mechanism consistently sinks the staples to the appropriate depth when fastening NM-B sheathed cable (14, 12, 10 AWG) and low voltage cables, supporting peak stapling productivity. Only compatible with our 1 in. insulated staples (sold separately), the M12 cable stapler gives the user the run-time needed to sink up to 1,200 staples on a fully charged M12 CP2.0ah battery.

Product Name: Milwaukee M18 FUEL 9 Ga. Utility Fencing Stapler
Description:
The Milwaukee M18 Fuel Utility Fencing Stapler delivers unmatched performance in a completely battery-powered solution. By leveraging our nitrogen spring technology, Powerstate brushless motor, and Redlink intelligence, this stapler delivers the power to seat staples into the toughest utility pole and fence post materials. Our M18 Fuel utility fencing stapler provides our users a 6X increase in productivity and a reduction in peak muscle effort compared to manual staple installation. Our cordless stapler is designed for compatibility with our 9 gauge galvanized staples (sold separately) available in three sizes: 1-1/2 in., 1-/4 in., 2 in. When paired with our M18 Redlithium CP3.0 battery pack, this stapler gives users the ability to sink up to 600 staples per charge. Our M18 Fuel utility fencing stapler joins the M18 system of over 200 solutions and is compatible with all M18 Redlithium batteries.
Fires 2 staples per second

Reversible belt hook - clip the nailer either to the right or left side of your belt, depending on your personal preference
Dry fire lockout - prevents accidental firing without nails loaded
Integrated lanyard loop ensures easy transfer and storage
Manual trigger lock - prevents accidental misfire and enhances the tool control

Product Name: Milwaukee M12 23 Ga. Finishing Pin Nailer
Description:
The Milwaukee M12 23-gauge pin nailer is the most compact cordless pin nailer, combining precision and power to deliver the performance that professional carpenters and remodelers demand, without the hassle of a compressor hose or gas cartridge. The 23-gauge pin nailer provides users with unmatched productivity and accessibility in tight spaces and confined corners with a lightweight, ergonomic design. The nitrogen air spring mechanism allows the nailer to consistently sink pin nails at proper depth into hard or softwoods while leaving small, clean nail holes. The double-action trigger and non-marring precision point tip allow users to perform sequential driving and accurate pin placement into delicate trim pieces. The dry-fire lockout feature prevents misfires and workpiece damage. The M12 pin nailer drives 23-Gauge headless pin nails ranging in length from 1/2 in. to 1-3/8 in. when paired with an M12 Redlithium CP1.5 battery pack.
Tool-free drive depth adjustment
Magazine reload indicator and dry fire lockout mechanism
LED light for increased visibility
Reversible belt hook - clip the nailer either to the right or left side of your belt, depending on your personal preference
Up to 750 Pin Nails Per Charge

Product Name: Milwaukee M18 FUEL 18 Volt Brushless 21 deg Framing Nailer
Description:
The Milwaukee M18 Fuel 21 degree framing nailer sets the new standard for cordless framing nailers. By leveraging a nitrogen spring mechanism, Powerstate brushless motor and Redlink Intelligence, this nailer provides users with pneumatic performance and the convenience and freedom of cordless power. Delivering the power to sink full round head nails into dense engineered lumbers, this framing nailer enables users to tackle even the most demanding framing applications. To keep users productive and efficient throughout the day, the framing gun fires 3 nails per second with zero ramp-up time, meaning a nail is fired as soon as the user pulls the trigger. Additionally, the cordless framing nailer operates using only Milwaukee's Redlithium Batteries (sold seperately) and sealed compressed nitrogen to drive each nail, completely eliminating the cost of gas cartridges and maintenance associated with competitors' nailers. The M18 Fuel 21 degree framing nailer delivers the pneumatic performance and durability that professional carpenters and remodelers expect, without the hassle of a compressor and hose or gas cartridge.
Cost-effective - eliminates the ongoing expense of gas cartridges
Dry fire lockout - prevents accidental firing without nails loaded
On board hex key storage
Sequential and contact actuation firing modes
Tool free drive depth adjustment
REDLINK PLUS intelligence - provides optimized performance and overload protection using total system communication between tool, battery and charger
Powerstate brushless motor delivers longer life and higher performance
Belt hook and rafter hook provides convenient storage options while working

Product Name: Milwaukee M12 1 gal Vertical Portable Hand-Held Air Compressor 120 psi 0.25 HP
Description:
The MILWAUKEE M12 Compact Inflator is the fastest, cordless tire inflator, delivering fast, accurate and easy inflation with the portability to take it anywhere. The Milwaukee compact inflator is rated to deliver over 12 PSI for demanding applications like car, LT truck and compact equipment tires with ultimate power. The high-efficiency motor and pump top-off car tires in under 1 minute. The compact tire inflator features TrueFill auto shut-off technology that delivers highly accurate pressure, protects from overfill and automatically senses speed of fill to shut-off at the desired PSI. The portable tire inflator includes a large easy-to-read back-lit LCD, anti-vibration feet and 26in hose with an all brass Schrader chuck. The Milwaukee tire inflator includes a ball inflation needle, presta chuck, Schrader chuck and an inflator nozzle.
3-year limited warranty
Fastest Cordless Tire Inflator: Top-off a car tire in under 1 minute. (28 - 35 PSI)
Inflates car, LT truck, and compact equipment tires.
REDLINK Intelligence: TrueFill auto shut-off technology increases accuracy, protects from over-temp and over-fill.
High efficiency pump and motor for true 12 PSI capability.
Illuminated digital gauge with target and current pressure reading.
Fills a LT truck tire in under 4 minutes (3-45 PSI).
2, lbs. pulls force
Tool holds rivet in any orientation
Ergonomically designed for force reduction

The Milwaukee M18 Fuel 18ga brad nailer delivers peak productivity at the jobsite, providing users with unmatched nailing performance without the hassle of a compressor and hose. Leveraging a nitrogen air spring mechanism, the finish nailer enables users to consistently sink nails to the proper depth in hard and soft woods while leaving clean nail holes matching the head of the nail. The combination of Milwaukee's Powerstate brushless motor and Redlink plus Intelligence delivers users with unmatched fire rate with zero ramp-up time keeping them efficient throughout their day. Additionally, the cordless brad nailer operates using Milwaukee's Redlithium Batteries (sold  seperately) and sealed compressed nitrogen to drive each nail. The 18 gauge nailer is compact in size and very lightweight, providing users with unmatched access into tight spaces and limiting their fatigue throughout their day. The M18 Fuel 18ga Brad nailer delivers the pneumatic performance that professional carpenters and remodelers expect with the freedom and convenience of cordless.

Product Name: Craftsman 6 gal Pancake Portable Air Compressor 150 psi 0.8 HP
Description:
The Craftsman 150 PSI. The oil-Free Pancake Compressor is ideal to support multiple trim finishing nailers, small framing/roofing jobs, and all general inflation, blowing, and smaller SCFM air tools. It features two regulated, factory-installed air couplers to easily support two users. The compressor body is made with steel for strength and has an upgraded shroud and console cover to protect its vital components. It is designed to operate at or below 150 PSI and features an oil-free pump, eliminating the need for maintenance. This compressor has a low-amp, 120-Volt motor that starts easily in cold weather or with an extension cord. It is designed for portability at only 30 lbs. and features an integrated carry handle.

Durable, oil-free pump for long-life and no maintenance

Product Name: Craftsman 1/4 in. Air Compressor Accessory Kit 20 pc
Description:
The CRAFTSMAN 20-Piece Air Compressor Accessory Kit provides everything you need to get started with your air compressor. This comprehensive kit includes essential tools and fittings for inflating tires, sports balls, air mattresses, and more, as well as for dusting and cleaning surfaces. Equipped with a durable 25-ft recoil hose and standard 1/4-in NPT quick-connect fittings, the kit ensures secure connections between your air tools and compressor. Accessories include a tire pressure gauge, blow gun, safety nozzle, sport ball inflation needles, dual-chuck tire inflator, rubber and tapered nozzles, and thread sealant tape to prevent leaks. Ideal for home, garage, or workshop use, this kit simplifies air compressor tasks with high-quality components.
Includes essential accessories to equip your air compressor for various tasks like inflating, cleaning, and connecting tools
Perfect for inflating tires, sports balls, air mattresses, dusting surfaces, and connecting air tools
Recoil air hose connects to all included accessories with 3/8-in quick-connect fittings for added convenience
Features 1/4-in NPT male and female brass and steel quick-connect fittings for secure and reliable connections
Designed for use with air compressors for automotive, household, and recreational applications
Includes thread sealant tape to prevent air leaks and ensure secure fittings
Compact kit is easy to organize and store, keeping all accessories ready for immediate use
